<dl id="n08154d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n08" href="#n08154d">N08 (VI.B.6)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n08all.htm#n08154d"> 154(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Antiburghers </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: = Secession from the church of Scotland, one of the two opposed bodies of the &ldquo;Associate Synod&rdquo;. The Antiburghers declared the swearing of the burgess oath as sinful. They held their first meeting in 1747. </mm> </dd></dl>
